name: FREE Medical & Hospital Icons Set
description:
Inspired by some projects I've done in the past, where I created a few custom icons I decided to expand what I created and share the collection.


Download icon pack


Icon pack for quick launch of medical projects!

  • SVG and PNG icons included
  • Based on Material guidelines
  • Ideal for the Internet and mobile devices
  • Made with love :)
  • Free updates forever
